_sText:
Zm_undergarden
------
1 house
1 bunker w/4 rooms
1 water pool
------
The map is not so big but there are many good defending positions for the non zombies.
I have also made so even if you are in a good defending position there is a way for zombies to get you. 
------
A few secrets in the map but all of them should not take long to figure out.
------
Installation notes is included.
------
Its been very fun to make this map it has improved my skills in hammer editor greatly.
